  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/FSKit\/FSItem\/Attributes\/changeTime\ncrawled: 2026-03-10T15:46:34Z\n---\n\n# changeTime\n\n**Instance Property**\n\nThe item’s last-changed time.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nvar changeTime: timespec { get set }\n```\n\n## Discussion\n\nThis property represents `ctime`, the last time the item’s metadata changed.\n\n## Working with time attributes\n\n- **accessTime**: The item’s last-accessed time.\n- **modifyTime**: The item’s last-modified time.\n- **birthTime**: The item’s creation time.\n- **backupTime**: The item’s last-backup time.\n- **addedTime**: The item’s added time.\n\n",
